msgctxt "#31410"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SERVICE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup control of Kodi via UPnP and HTTP · Configure file sharing[CR]Enable Zeroconf · Configure AirPlay"
msgstr "[B] KONFIGUREER DIENSINSTELLINGS[/B][CR][CR]Opstelbeheer van Kodi via UPnP en HTTP · Stel lêerdeling op[CR]Aktiveer Zeroconf · Stel AirPlay op"

