msgctxt "#31414"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE PLAYER SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Configure video playback · Configure music playback · Configure picture slideshow[CR]Configure video language and subtitles"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGUREER SPELER-INSTELLINGS[/B][CR][CR]Konfigureer videoterugspeel · Stel musiekterugspeel op · Stel prentskyfievertoning op[CR]Konfigureer videotaal en onderskrifte"

msgctxt "#31415"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE MEDIA SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Set default select action · Configure file list options · Configure metadata options[CR]Manage databases"
msgstr "[B] KONFIGUREER MEDIA-INSTELLINGS[/B][CR][CR]Stel verstekkiesaksie · Stel lêerlysopsies op · Stel metadata-opsies op[CR]Bestuur databasisse"

msgctxt "#31421"
msgid "Select your Kodi user profile[CR]to login and continue"
msgstr "Kies jou Kodi-gebruikersprofiel[CR] om aan te meld en voort te gaan"

msgctxt "#31427"
msgid "Skin Shortcuts is responsible for handling all aspects of the main menu."
msgstr "Skin Shortcuts is verantwoordelik vir die hantering van alle aspekte van die hoofkieslys."

msgctxt "#31428"
msgid "The Grab Fanart script provides the random fanart slideshows for the main menu."
msgstr "Die Grab Fanart-skrip verskaf die ewekansige fanart-skyfievertonings vir die hoofkieslys."

msgctxt "#31429"
msgid "Library Data Provider is a service that runs in the background to provide library data for widgets and live backgrounds as well as playlist statistics for infolines."
msgstr "Biblioteekdataverskaffer is 'n diens wat in die agtergrond loop om biblioteekdata vir legstukke en lewendige agtergronde sowel as snitlysstatistieke vir inligtinglyne te verskaf."

msgctxt "#31430"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white studio icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Hulpbronbeeld-byvoeging om die verstek wit ateljee-ikone regdeur die vel te vertoon."

msgctxt "#31431"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white recording label icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Hulpbronbeeld-byvoeging om die verstek-wit opname-etiket-ikone regdeur die vel te vertoon."

msgctxt "#31432"
msgid "Provides numerous Widget options and extended cast and crew metadata."
msgstr "Verskaf talle Widget opsies en uitgebreide rolverdeling en bemanning metadata."

msgctxt "#31433"
msgid "Skin Info Service is used to display movie set information throughout the skin."
msgstr "Velinligtingdiens word gebruik om filmstelinligting regdeur die vel te vertoon."

msgctxt "#31434"
msgid "Check MP3 Theme checks whether the user has put a theme.mp3 file in the corresponding movie/TV show folder to be played when browsing."
msgstr "Kontroleer MP3-tema kontroleer of die gebruiker 'n tema.mp3-lêer in die ooreenstemmende fliek-/TV-programlêer geplaas het om gespeel te word wanneer hy blaai."

msgctxt "#31450"
msgid "  •  Open Settings "
msgstr "• Maak Instellings oop"

msgctxt "#31451"
msgid "  •  Click to Install"
msgstr "• Klik om te installeer"

msgctxt "#31473"
msgid "Aeon Tajo Helper provides the data to display the cast for movies and TV shows."
msgstr "Aeon Tajo Helper verskaf die data om die rolverdeling vir flieks en TV-programme te vertoon."

msgctxt "#31474"
msgid "CU LRC Lyrics is used to download, sync, and display lyrics during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "CU LRC Lyrics word gebruik om lirieke af te laai, te sinkroniseer en te vertoon tydens volskermmusiekspeel."

msgctxt "#31475"
msgid "Play Trailer makes possible to play movie trailers through a context menu. "
msgstr "Play Trailer maak dit moontlik om flieksleepwaens deur 'n kontekskieslys te speel."

msgctxt "#31476"
msgid "Allows the use of Youtube to play trailers and other videos."
msgstr "Laat die gebruik van Youtube toe om sleepwaens en ander video's te speel."

msgctxt "#31477"
msgid "Provides some cast actress images to be shown in video views."
msgstr "Verskaf 'n paar rolverdeling-aktrise-beelde om in video-aansigte gewys te word."

msgctxt "#31478"
msgid "Artist Slideshow is used to display artist fanart for both the home screen and during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Kunstenaarskyfievertoning word gebruik om kunstenaarsfankuns vir beide die tuisskerm en tydens volskermmusiekspeel te vertoon."

msgctxt "#31479"
msgid "AutoCompletion provides suggestions to be selected while using the virtual keyboard."
msgstr "Outovoltooiing verskaf voorstelle wat gekies moet word terwyl die virtuele sleutelbord gebruik word."

msgctxt "#31480"
msgid "Library Editor Script uses JSON to directly edit your database information."
msgstr "Library Editor Script gebruik JSON om jou databasisinligting direk te wysig."

msgctxt "#31481"
msgid "Global Search makes possible to search among all the items (movies, TV shows, music, actors, etc.) in your collection."
msgstr "Global Search maak dit moontlik om tussen al die items (flieks, TV-programme, musiek, akteurs, ens.) in jou versameling te soek."

