msgctxt "#31290"
msgid "Thanks for using Aeon Tajo—I really hope you’re enjoying it. Creating and maintaining a Kodi skin like this takes hundreds of hours of work. If Aeon Tajo is something you enjoy and find useful, supporting it helps me keep working on it and ensures it can continue evolving in the future. [CR][CR]If you decide to do so, you’ll receive frequent updates with new features and bug fixes, along with videos, media packs, and easy-to-follow articles with detailed tips to help you get the most out of everything Aeon Tajo has to offer, together with my sincere gratitude for your support. [CR][CR]For more information, visit [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] and search for the creator [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], or go to [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Thanks!"
msgstr "Dankie dat jy Aeon Tajo gebruik - ek hoop regtig jy geniet dit.Om 'n Kodi-vel soos hierdie te skep en in stand te hou, verg honderde ure se werk.As Aeon Tajo iets is wat jy geniet en nuttig vind, help dit my om daaraan te bly werk en verseker dit dat dit in die toekoms kan voortgaan om te ontwikkel.[CR][CR]As jy besluit om dit te doen, sal jy gereelde opdaterings ontvang met nuwe kenmerke en foutoplossings, saam met video's, mediapakkette en maklik-om-te-volg artikels met gedetailleerde wenke om jou te help om die meeste uit alles wat Aeon Tajo bied te kry, tesame met my opregte dankbaarheid vir jou ondersteuning.[CR][CR]Vir meer inligting, besoek [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] en soek vir die skepper [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], of gaan na [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[CR]]/B.][CR!/C!"

